## Few-shot examples

**Example 1 — Click a primary button:**
```python
WebDriverWait(driver, 10).until(
    EC.element_to_be_clickable((By.ID, "submit-btn"))
).click()
```

**Example 2 — Fill an input and submit a form:**
```python
WebDriverWait(driver, 10).until(EC.visibility_of_element_located((By.ID, "email"))).send_keys("user@example.com")
driver.find_element(By.ID, "password").send_keys("secret")
driver.find_element(By.CSS_SELECTOR, "form button[type='submit']").click()
```

**Example 3 — Assert text after navigation:**
```python
WebDriverWait(driver, 10).until(
    EC.text_to_be_present_in_element((By.CSS_SELECTOR, "[data-test-id=order-status]"), "CONFIRMED")
)
```

